<paragraph id="8BFD36D586066B20FA9D8875F81DFBCD" blockId="20.[1300,2282,565,1663]" pageId="20" pageNumber="83">Stratigraphic position. In bioclastic limestone, upper part of the Dangarfield Formation.</paragraph>
